desc_long							评测						“If you're a sucker for realistic physics in games, enjoy solving puzzles or display both of those traits, you're going to love it.”75 – Mouse N Joypad“This is a game every puzzle fan should play!”9 – 3RD STRIKE“The art style is extremely appealing with an upbeat soundtrack that creates a very beautiful feeling game”7 – TechRaptor												关于这款游戏							Bloop is back and it’s bigger and better than ever!Your favourite chemistry potions puzzler is back in Bloop Reloaded and ready to test the brain cells like never before.  Make sure you save as much of the potions as possible.  How you do it is up to you!Features27 LevelsBuild Paths and guide your potions to safety.Use environmental physics to your advantage.There is no one correct solution, just the limits of your creative mind!See what happens when you mix potions.Create your own levels						
